HEADWORD: futz
<hw>futz</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To fool around; to act without plan
or purpose; -- usually used with <ptcl>around</ptcl>; <as>as, don't
<ex>futz around</ex> with a device without understanding its
operation</as>.</def> <mark>[Slang.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

